text: Jang Jun-young (; born 4 February 1993) is a South Korean footballer who plays as defender for Suwon FC. ==Career== Jang joined K League Challenge side Daejeon Citizen in January 2016. ==References== == External links == * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Association football defenders Category:South Korean footballers Category:Daejeon Hana Citizen FC players Category:Seongnam FC players Category:Suwon FC players Category:Korea National League players Category:K League 2 players
